Sri Lanka Defers Monetary Policy Announcement, Gunaratna Says

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-06-06T08:20:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/sri-lanka-defers-monetary-policy-announcement-gunaratna-says.html
Sri Lanka ’s monthly monetary policy
announcement has been deferred to June 14, Swarna Gunaratna,
additional director of the central bank’s economic research
department, said by telephone today.  The policy statement was to be released on June 10 earlier.
The review has been delayed because the monetary board meeting
was rescheduled, according to Gunaratna.  To contact the reporter on this story:
